# Frontend Deploy Standard

- Never build the frontend on IQHost. The Git hook environment does not have `npm`.
- Do not commit `dist/` artifacts for production publish.
- For `coach.host89998.iqhs.pl`, standard flow is local `npm run build`, then `.\deploy-front.ps1`.
- `deploy-front.ps1` sends local `dist/*` to `/home/host89998/domains/coach.host89998.iqhs.pl/public_html/` through SCP.
- The server-side `post-receive` hook is only for backend checkout/deploy; it must not run `npm ci` or `npm run build`.
- If the frontend looks stale in production, first verify that the local `dist/*` was copied to `public_html/`.
- For production build configuration, ensure `/.env.production` provides `VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.coach.host89998.iqhs.pl/api`.
